Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  到了哦  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.15,0:03:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.62,0:03:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好难受的  小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.53,0:03:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤肉天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃真精神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.62,0:04:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博真没精神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小铃的兴致太高了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.84,0:04:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服吧  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.91,0:04:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  集合~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们自己来准备材料吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.27,0:04:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼当然要新鲜的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.83,0:04:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.18,0:04:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好大一条
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大收获
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.23,0:04:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也钓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好  小要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.45,0:04:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.50,0:05:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钓到了  钓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.38,0:05:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  博士君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼都不去博士君那里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说了会分给他的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.17,0:05:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥真是的  好像较上劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小博
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.29,0:05:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别钓了  回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.72,0:05:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没有见到那么高兴的麻奈了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  这里真是个好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.17,0:05:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前说过的嫦娥狼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:06:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前似乎也是生活在这一带的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.83,0:06:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们所居住的城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全被包围在森林和自然中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.90,0:06:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.12,0:06:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总觉得好像是被关起来了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被这名为自然的巨大笼子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？那个…说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧  博士君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.16,0:06:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一脸当真的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是因为要同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.37,0:06:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是诗歌  诗歌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…听起来不像是诗歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.55,0:06:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  小铃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到刚才还在这里组装烤肉架来着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.51,0:06:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微去找一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.47,0:07:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么只有衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现变态  发现变态
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始击退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个装扮怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可大意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌呀  小博不要这样盯着看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.97,0:07:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  为什么是泳装
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是来烤肉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.11,0:07:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士君  找到小铃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.33,0:07:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要同学你来说说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃居然穿泳装…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管那么多  过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没带泳装来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.89,0:07:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣裤好不容易才干的说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.13,0:07:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得那么好的天气  马上就会干的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.58,0:07:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么乱来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.93,0:07:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博生气了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.41,0:08:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.78,0:08:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博真的对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  不用这样道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  做了错事就要好好道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.90,0:08:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以小博  就以此原谅我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗  原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.58,0:08:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你相信小铃的话了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的以为我会让你看了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.13,0:08:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.39,0:08:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  不要戏弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  八朔是拿来当点心？还是要烤？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.15,0:09:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤？怎么可能做那种遭天谴的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭天谴…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那在八朔上画脸就不会遭天谴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我专用的特别标志
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.50,0:09:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行  快盖上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃得好饱  好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都吃完了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会儿去称下体重  脸就会发青了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.86,0:10:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真是美味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢烧烤了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.48,0:10:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后再来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.85,0:10:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我洗过后再送还
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意  就这样好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样博士君的气味就会留下了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.85,0:10:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又说奇怪的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.06,0:10:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的  开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.82,0:10:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥的玩笑有时很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.51,0:10:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赌上小博的衣服和我决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.33,0:10:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃也够奇怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:10:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别擅自拿我赌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是累坏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.65,0:11:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  今天真是谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.96,0:11:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用这样道谢的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.51,0:11:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和博士君在一起我也很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.60,0:11:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是要感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.36,0:11:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  小铃钓到了那么大的鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.15,0:11:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而哥哥却一条都没钓到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.91,0:11:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天只是手感不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.97,0:11:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人  连鱼饵的蚯蚓都不敢拿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.55,0:11:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要让小铃来替你上饵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.45,0:12:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧  小博
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.05,0:12:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻涕流个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑子也有点晕晕的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是发烧了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.54,0:12:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  都是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.39,0:12:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天还算勉强撑过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.07,0:12:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来非得好好道个歉不可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博  作为赔礼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.87,0:12:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.02,0:12:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可真无力吐槽了  现在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.72,0:12:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病得不轻呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.26,0:12:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去「中心」一趟？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.81,0:12:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「中心」？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.87,0:12:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是「嫦娥医疗中心」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.54,0:12:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一家综合性医院  我们都叫它「中心」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面最新设备一应俱全
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.07,0:12:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是家挺有规模的医院
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.11,0:12:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  还是去看看医生比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.53,0:12:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  我就跟你一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:12:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.48,0:13:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人也能去的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.97,0:13:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是小铃你在医院里被传染了感冒什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.61,0:13:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不好办了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.04,0:13:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  路上小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.38,0:13:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃  你保护过头了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的跟要同学说的一样  好大呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  来这儿的人也真不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.74,0:13:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄博士先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.28,0:13:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.24,0:13:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有劳您了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.89,0:14:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.19,0:14:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是九澄博士对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.27,0:14:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的事情  我已经从侄女那儿听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.75,0:14:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侄女？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.76,0:14:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉名田…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眠她是我的侄女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.89,0:14:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听眠说  班上新转来了个奇怪的同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「奇怪的同学」…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.87,0:14:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没什么  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.63,0:14:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在本人面前说他是「奇怪的同学」  的确有些失礼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒啊  要不要先验个血？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,验血？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也给你开了些药  回去的时候去药店取吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.88,0:14:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  就开始抽血吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.23,0:14:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是要回去？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.21,0:14:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是方便的话  一起如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.55,0:15:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是院长栉名田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.98,0:15:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下贤木
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.57,0:15:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得你们生物制药公司的负责人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.56,0:15:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是境井先生才对啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  不过从今以后  就都由在下来接洽了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.30,0:15:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这交接可真突然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一些公司内部的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给您添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.54,0:15:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没的事  没的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.14,0:15:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下手上的这份  姑且就算是敝社的产品介绍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「姑且」这话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好像有点缺乏职业作风呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的  敝社预定今后要加大新药的研发力度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.62,0:15:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想  这或许能够对院长您的研究有所助益
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.58,0:15:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定不负厚望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.79,0:15:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.53,0:16:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.57,0:16:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃她给你添麻烦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一诚前辈也感冒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.71,0:16:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我是来取一些常用的药的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常用的药？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  是不是哪里有…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.19,0:16:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在担心我的身体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士君你可真会体贴人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.70,0:16:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.65,0:16:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  博士君…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.84,0:16:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和小铃她  已经吻过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.21,0:16:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「难不成」  是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说  难不成  你对女孩子不感兴趣之类的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那种事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你看啊  虽说是我这个做哥的一面之词吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.22,0:16:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃她也确实挺漂亮的对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.18,0:16:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.50,0:16:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可尽管如此  尽管她对你是那样的穷追不舍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对她却仍旧是坐怀不乱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.69,0:16:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.69,0:16:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是挺奇怪的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？这路没走错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.57,0:17:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一诚前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有什么要紧事赶着回去办呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.75,0:17:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍微兜了下风而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.08,0:17:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实  我是想能够像这样  与你单独相处
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.59,0:17:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.42,0:17:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士君你的香味…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.17,0:17:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  哎…！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.81,0:17:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.34,0:17:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？  啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.43,0:17:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住…  住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…  不要…  啊…  啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…  不行…  你…  住手啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:17:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.99,0:18:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.43,0:18:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  啊…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.44,0:18:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是开个玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.89,0:18:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.97,0:18:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.12,0:18:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绿灯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.56,0:18:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃她也有说过  你很容易上当呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:18:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天  那孩子来了医院一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那孩子」是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.55,0:19:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄博士么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.98,0:19:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.14,0:19:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确  跟小眠你说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏又是在这个八朔收成不好的年景里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.63,0:19:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了个那样的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.07,0:19:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.05,0:19:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道小眠你也不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.12,0:19:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.79,0:20:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.34,0:20:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是让一诚大哥送你回来的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.24,0:20:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥你也太偷奸耍滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.35,0:20:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.99,0:20:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是也发了烧  去了医院就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.83,0:20:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可真能说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.12,0:20:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都说什么「去了反而身体会更不好」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？  有这事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.64,0:20:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  朝三暮四
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.77,0:20:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不早点睡可对身体不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.80,0:20:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我弄醒的好像就是你吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.34,0:21:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧退了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  已经好了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.02,0:21:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.56,0:21:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可别大意了  还是吃点药比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.10,0:21:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.50,0:21:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.46,0:21:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.76,0:21:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧好像退了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.51,0:21:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀  似乎还有那么点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.90,0:21:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经好了啦
